        <Summary>FUSE filesystem for transcoding FLAC to MP3 on the fly</Summary>
        <Description>MP3FS is a read-only FUSE filesystem which transcodes audio formats (currently FLAC) to MP3 on the fly when opened and read. It is also a novel alternative to traditional mp3 encoder applications. Users can use their favorite file browser to select the files they want encoded and copy them somewhere.</Description>
